item.title: How to log in?
item.dc:creator: @RandQm RandQm
item.description:
@RandQm wrote:

demon hunt3r:

I just found out about moparscape. How do I log into someone’s server? Everytime I try to log in it says error connecting or something of that nature.

I suppose you was trying to utilize the moparscape client.
You need to either be running a server on your local host to play local, or put the ip of a server you wish to play.
Note that a lot of server are only compatible with their own client.
